<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning, Raffae=
lla.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hope you are well t=
his morning.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive the=
 $9,000 temporary accommodation payment in 3 to 5 working days.</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The remaining amount=
 under the temporary accommodation benefit is $13,820.62</span><o:p></o:p></=
p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is there a time I ca=
n contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents claim? the loss s=
chedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum insured, which me=
ans that the contents is a total
 loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is greater the=
n the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week suits you=
.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have confirmation t=
hat your privacy request and the information you requested was emailed to yo=
u on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me know if you have it=
.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding updates, I=
 am more then happy to update you on the first of each month, would you pref=
er monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding further cl=
aim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive these from the ass=
essor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the entire claim file e=
ach month and not efficient for us
 due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting assessor rep=
orts during this process which means that report may not be added to that pr=
ivacy request.
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Future assessor repo=
rts should be the only documents we have that you are not given by the asses=
sor as this would come from us.</span><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-fa=
mily:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:#001272;mso-ligatures:standardcont=
extual">
